## General rules
- This is an MCP server repository
- Write code in english language
- Write comments and documents in english language
- If you don't know the answer to a request, say so instead of making something up.
- Always verify generated code and remove unused functions, fix linting errors
- Run `cr review --plain` to get comprehensive code analysis and improvement suggestions. Apply the feedback to write cleaner, more maintainable code.

